OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773245482
OL,3,CIrish book-keeper wins #23,000 over
OL,4,Cboss's 'potato' slurs
OL,6,FA book-keeper whose boss repeatedly
OL,7,Fshouted the word "potato" at her "in a
OL,8,Fstrong Irish accent" has won more than
OL,9,F#23,000 after an employment tribunal
OL,10,Ffound she had been racially harassed.
OL,12,FBernadette Hayes, who is Irish,
OL,13,Fdescribed suffering "a death by 1,000
OL,14,Fcuts" between December 2023 and June
OL,15,F2024 while working for engineering
OL,16,Fcompany West Leeds Civils.
OL,18,FWest Leeds Civils is a multi-service
OL,19,Fconstruction and civil engineering
OL,20,Fcompany based in Holbeck.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773245482
OL,3,CIrish book-keeper wins #23,000 over
OL,4,Cboss's 'potato' slurs
OL,6,FThe firm's director Mick Atkins also
OL,7,Fused the terms "paddy", "stupid paddy"
OL,8,Fand "pikey", Leeds employment tribunal
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FA judge ruled that the "offensive and
OL,12,Fhumiliating" phrases are "overtly
OL,13,Flinked to race" before awarding the
OL,14,Fclaimant #20,735.91 and ordering the
OL,15,Fbusiness to give her four weeks' pay,
OL,16,Famounting to #2,800.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773245482
OL,3,CIrish book-keeper wins #23,000 over
OL,4,Cboss's 'potato' slurs
OL,6,FOutlining her claim, Ms Hayes said:
OL,7,F"Throughout my time at West Leeds
OL,8,FCivils, Mr Atkins did make occasional
OL,9,Fcomments about me being Irish. Most in
OL,10,Fgest (sic), and whilst I knew it was
OL,11,Fwrong, I tried to accept it as humour."
OL,13,FBut she said his behaviour "ramped up"
OL,14,Fafter his friend Marcus Smith became
OL,15,Finvolved in the business.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773245482
OL,3,CIrish book-keeper wins #23,000 over
OL,4,Cboss's 'potato' slurs
OL,6,FMs Hayes, who was 55 at the time,
OL,7,Fcontinued: "If we had a disagreement,
OL,8,Fhe would shout 'potato' in a strong
OL,9,FIrish accent over and over again. He
OL,10,Fdone this in front of other members of
OL,11,Fstaff. He would shout 'potato' as soon
OL,12,Fas he walked in the office without me
OL,13,Fhaving even spoke to him.
OL,15,F"This totally eroded my self-respect
OL,16,Fand my self-esteem. It made me feel
OL,17,Fsmall, insecure, violated and
OL,18,Fextremely anxious. It also made me
OL,19,Ffeel embarrassed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773245482
OL,3,CIrish book-keeper wins #23,000 over
OL,4,Cboss's 'potato' slurs
OL,6,F"I had a huge change in my personal
OL,7,Fcircumstances and I needed my job. I
OL,8,Ffelt trapped and this added to my
OL,9,Fanxiety. I used to remain quiet so as
OL,10,Fnot to draw attention to myself but
OL,11,Feven this did not work.
OL,13,F"He even sent potato in a WhatsApp
OL,14,Fexchange.
OL,16,F"Mr Atkins further called me a gypsy/
OL,17,Ftraveller due to my Irish heritage. He
OL,18,Fwould constantly say that I was
OL,19,Flusting after the travellers outside
OL,20,Fthe office.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773245482
OL,3,CIrish book-keeper wins #23,000 over
OL,4,Cboss's 'potato' slurs
OL,6,FI felt bullied and harassed by this."
OL,8,FEmployment Judge Buckley found that Ms
OL,9,FHayes told Mr Atkins "on a number of
OL,10,Foccasions" that she did not find his
OL,11,Fcomments funny.
OL,13,FThe judge accepted that Ms Hayes did
OL,14,F"join in" on two occasions by using
OL,15,Fthe word potato or the potato emoji in
OL,16,Fmessages, but that she did it to "fit
OL,17,Fin" and "make it seem OK".
OL,19,FThe book-keeper took sick leave in
OL,20,FJuly 2024, messaging Mr Atkins: "I do
OL,21,Fwant to leave, I am sorry.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773245482
OL,3,CIrish book-keeper wins #23,000 over
OL,4,Cboss's 'potato' slurs
OL,6,F"Life is too short and I have been
OL,7,Funhappy for some time, and it's not
OL,8,Ffair on either of us to let that
OL,9,Fcontinue."
OL,11,FShe raised a grievance about Mr
OL,12,FSmith's behaviour, which the tribunal
OL,13,Fheard she described as "bullish",
OL,14,Fbefore raising a further complaint of
OL,15,Findirect harassment related to a
OL,16,Fprotected characteristic.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773245482
OL,3,CIrish book-keeper wins #23,000 over
OL,4,Cboss's 'potato' slurs
OL,6,FIn a document setting out her
OL,7,Fgrievance, she said: "The last six
OL,8,Fmonths at this job has made me feel
OL,9,Flike I have suffered a death by 1,000
OL,10,Fcuts.
OL,12,F"Due to working in a hostile and toxic
OL,13,Fenvironment my GP signed me off work
OL,14,Fwith work-related stress on 29th July
OL,15,F2024. This is after months of
OL,16,Fharassment and bullying.
OL,18,F"I passionately believe that this was
OL,19,Fcaused by the actions of Mr Atkins
OL,20,F(and) Mr Smith."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773245482
OL,3,CIrish book-keeper wins #23,000 over
OL,4,Cboss's 'potato' slurs
OL,6,FMs Hayes was later dismissed from the
OL,7,Fcompany.
OL,9,FJudge Buckley said in a judgment: "I
OL,10,Fhave accepted the impact that this
OL,11,Fconduct had on the claimant.
OL,13,F"From a subjective point of view, it
OL,14,Fclearly created a hostile, humiliating
OL,15,Fand offensive environment for her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773245482
OL,3,CIrish book-keeper wins #23,000 over
OL,4,Cboss's 'potato' slurs
OL,6,F"In my view, taken as a whole, it is
OL,7,Freasonable for an individual of Irish
OL,8,Fheritage to find the repeated use of
OL,9,Fthe terms 'potato', 'paddy', 'stupid
OL,10,Fpaddy' and 'pikey' offensive and
OL,11,Fhumiliating.
OL,13,F"These phrases are overtly linked to
OL,14,Frace, particularly when considered
OL,15,Ftogether rather than in isolation. On
OL,16,Fthat basis I find that the conduct was
OL,17,Flinked to race.
OL,19,F"On that basis the harassment claim
OL,20,Fsucceeds."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
